00:18:14.890 --> 00:18:17.590
One thing that you can do
is that you just give

00:18:17.720 --> 00:18:21.230
the link tag

00:18:21.300 --> 00:18:23.110
on the author byline

00:18:24.470 --> 00:18:28.640
that index of higher
