00:21:56.070 --> 00:21:59.240
but it makes it
so that the text is not selectable

00:21:59.970 --> 00:22:03.140
because it's like the pseudo-element
is on top of, for example, here

00:22:03.210 --> 00:22:05.710
the paragraph
and if somebody wants to select

00:22:05.810 --> 00:22:09.550
this paragraph description
and copy it somewhere, it doesn't work.

00:22:10.180 --> 00:22:12.380
I must admit that I personally,

00:22:12.380 --> 00:22:15.280
