00:38:54.580 --> 00:38:59.590
in the card, make them clickable
by raising them above the pseudo-element

00:38:59.720 --> 00:39:03.390
with Z-index
and adding padding to reduce mis-taps.

00:39:04.330 --> 00:39:08.260
Also, make it clear what the card does
with a descriptive call to action

00:39:08.660 --> 00:39:11.600
connected to the link
with ARIA-describe-by.

00:39:13.270 --> 00:39:15.740
Add focus on hover styles
to the whole card.

00:39:16.670 --> 00:39:19.740
Add empty alt text
if the image is decorative.

00:39:20.410 --> 00:39:23.580
Add alt text for any images
that add important information

00:39:23.680 --> 00:39:26.180
and in that case, consider changing

00:39:26.520 --> 00:39:29.020
if the image is before

00:39:29.520 --> 00:39:31.650
the headline,

00:39:31.750 --> 00:39:34.220
